      "raw_text": "SALT LAKE, Nov. 15--It is an.\nnounced by Director Holden that\nthe smelter of the United States\nSmelling & Refining Co. at Bing-\nham Junction, which employs 1000\nmen, will be closed down at once.\nThe affirmation by the United\nStates court of appeals Of the de-\ncision against the smelters in the\nsmoke\" cases is the reason given\nfor the closing down. This is likely\nto have a serious effect OF the min\ning industry of this state."
    }
  ]
